                            <comment id="14545828" author="prr" created="Thu, 15 Dec 2022 13:26:52 -0800"  >I have Windows 11 with an Nvidia Quadro P2000.&lt;br/&gt;
I launched SwingSet2 with a recent JDK mainline build, then put my PC to sleep&lt;br/&gt;
Start Menu-&amp;gt;Power-&amp;gt;Sleep&lt;br/&gt;
